\id HEB  
\ide UTF-8
\h Ba Hibbulu 
\toc1 Ba Hibbulu 
\toc2 Ba Hibbulu 
\toc3 heb 
\mt1 Ba Hibbulu  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Chiindi chakale Leza wakaambula kuli basikale besu kwiinda muba sinsimi muzyiindi zyiingi alimwi amunzila zyiingi.  
\v 2 Pesi muli aaya mazuba aamamanino wakaambula kulindiswe kwiinda mumwana mulombe, ooyo ngwaakayimikizya kuti akabesikulya lukonowezintu zyoonse. Nkwiindila mulinguwe alubo Leza wakachita bwaanze.  
\v 3 We ngusikubalangala kwabulemu bwa Leza. Bwiiminizi bulimbubo bwabwiime bwakwe. Aboobo ulajata zinti zyoonse amwii ajwi lyamanguzu aakwe. Naakamana kusanzya zibi, wakakkala aansi kululyo lwabupati kujulu.  
\v 4 Wakaba ulanguzu kubangelo mbuli zina ndyakakona liluleme kwiinda aabo mazina.  
\v 5 Nkaambo nkuli uuli wabangelo Leza ngwakatgi “Uli mwana wangu, sunu ndaba wuso”? Nakuti nguuli wabangelo Leza ngwakati, “Ndiyoba wisi kulinguwe alimwi we uyoba mwana kulindime”?  
\v 6 Pesi lubo aawo Leza nayeta mwana mutaanzi munyika, we utii, “Boonse bangelo mba Leza beelede kumukomba.”  
\v 7 Aatala abangelo utii, “Nguwe uuchita bangelo bakwe babe myuuya, mpawo balanda bakwe babe malabi amulilo  
\v 8 Pesi aatala amwana utuu, “Chuuno chakwe, Leza, chikkala mane kukabe kutamani. Lubeteko lwabwami bwako ndubeteko lwabululami.  
\v 9 Wakayanda bulumi mpawo wasula kutabaamba mulawu. Nkunkaako webo Leza wako wakunanika amafuta aalukondo kwiinda beenzinyokwe.”  
\v 10 “Kumatalikilo, Mwami wakayala matalisyo aanyika. Majulu milimo yamaboko aako.  
\v 11 Bayoonyonyooka, pesi uyooyinkila kunembo. Bayoozakala boonse mbuli chimpanzi chasila.  
\v 12 Uyobavunga mbuli chizwaato mpawo bayosandulwa mbuli chimpanzi chasila. Pesi webo tosanduki, amyaaka yako tiimani.”  
\v 13 Mpesi kuli ooyo bangelo ba Leza bakati amulichili chiikndi, “Kkala kululyo lwangu mane ndikachite basinkondonyokwe bakabe chilyatilizyo chamawulu aako.”?  
\v 14 Teensi bangelo boonse myuuya iibeleka na, abaabo bakatumwa kutabilila aabo bayokona lufutuko?   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Aboobo tweelede kuswilisisya kuleezyo nzitwakamvwa kuti tutaka sosoloki kulinzizyo.  
\v 2 Nkaambo naa makani akaambwa kubangelo akaboneka kuti ngakusinizya, akuti zibi zyoonse akutaswiilila zipegw chisubulo.  
\v 3 Nga tulachija biyeni kuti twawuzya kulufutuko luli boobu? Olu ndulufutuko lwakatalika kwaambilizigwa a Mwami akuzuminwa kulindiswe abaabo bakalumvwa.  
\v 4 Muchiindi nchicheecho Leza wapa bukamboni, azitondeezyo azigambyo, amaleele asiyene siyen, akwaabila zipo akwaabila zipo zya Muuya Uusalala mbuli kuyanda kwakwe  
\v 5 Nkaambo teensi nkubangelo Leza nkwaka bombya nyika kuti isike, atala anzitwaambula.  
\v 6 Pesi umwi wakaba kamboni kumwi, kaamba kuti, “Niinzi chitegwa muntu ooyo ngumuyeeya aatala anguwe? Na mwana wamuntu ooyo ngumulikatazya aawe?  
\v 7 Wakachita kuti muntu abe ansi kubangelo, wakamusamika bulemu akulemekwa. amwi malembe mapati achiindi achi Giliki alayungizya, alimwi wakamubika aatala yamilimu yamaanza aakwe.  
\v 8 Wakabika zykooknse mukuzibombya munsi lyazituta zyakwe.” Nkaambo nguwe Leza ngwakabikka qkuzintu zykoonse eezi. Pesi lino tatunazibona pe zyoonse nzyakabikilwa  
\v 9 Pesi tulikumubona ooyo wakabikidwe kunsi kubangelo, muchiindi chiniini Jesu, wakasamikwa bulemu akulemekwa nkaambo kamapenzi aalufu lwakwe kuti muluzyalo lwa Leza akalabizye lufu lwabantu boonse.  
\v 10 Nkaambo chaleelede kuti Leza, nkaambo zyoonse ziponena nguwe kwiinda mulinguwe, kuti alete myuuya yoonse kubulemu. Chakeelela kulinguwe kuti abe ntalisyo yalufutuko kiizwide kwiindila mukupenzegwa kwakwe.  
\v 11 Nkaambo ooyo uusalazya abasalizigwa boonse bazwa kumwi. Nkikaako tawuusi pe kubiita kuti banabakwabo.  
\v 12 Waamba kuti, “Ndiyolungulula zina lyako kubana bakwesu, ndiyoyimba atala anduwe mukati mumbungano.”  
\v 13 Alubo, “Ndiyoosyoma mulinguwe,” alubo “Amulange, mpaano mpebede abana mbaakandipa Leza.”  
\v 14 Aboobo, mbulikuti bana ba Leza banyama abulowa bomwe, Jesu alakwe wakali umwi kuzintu zyiingi ambabo, kuchitila kuti mulufu akakonzye kuzunda ooyo wakali aamanguzu alufu, ooyo, kudyabbulosi.  
\v 15 Chakaba oobo kuti akaangunune boonse abao bakaba akuyoowa lufu balkapona buumi bwabo boonse mubuzike.  
\v 16 Nkaambo nchoonzyo tanyongani nkaambo kabangelo pe; pesi; ulanyongana loko kumbuto ya Abbulahamu.  
\v 17 Aboobo chakaleelede kuti akabe mbuli bana bakwabo munzila zyoonse, kuchitila kuti akabe mupayizi uusyomekede alimwi uulaluzyalo mubulyidilano azintu zya Leza, akuti akakonzye kweeta lulekelelo kuzibi zyapbantu.  
\v 18 Nkaambo Jesu lwakwe wakapenzegwa mumasunko, ulakonzya kugwasiya aabo balikusunkwa.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 Aboobo, nobakwesu basalala, anywebo muli aalukono mulwiito lwakujulu. Amuyeeye Jesu, mutumwa alimwi kali mupayizi mupati waluzumino lwesu.  
\v 2 Wakalisyomekede kuli Leza, wakamusala, mbuli mbaakasyomekede alakwe Mozesi mung'anda ya Leza.  
\v 3 Nkaambo Jesu wakajanika kali musalali abulemu bupati kwiinda bwa Mozesi, nkaambo ooyo uuyaka ng'anda ujana bulemu kwiinda ng'anda lwayo.  
\v 4 Nkaambo ang'anda ang'anda ilamuntu uyiyaka, pesi wakayaka zyoonse ngu Leza.  
\v 5 Kulilimbi bbazu, Mozesi wakali zyomekede mung'anda ya Leza yoonse. Walkali kaamboni aatala azintu zyalikuzowambulwa mulilya juunza.  
\v 6 Pesi Kkilisito mwana mweendelezi wang'anda ya Lez. Tuli ng'anda yakwe, na twajatisya kubusichaamba bwesu akubotelwa mukusima kwesu.  
\v 7 Aboobo, zilimbuli mbawamba Muuya Uusalala uti: “Sunu na mwalimvwa jwi lyakwe  
\v 8 mutayumyi myoyo yanu mbuli mulupapi, muchiindi chakusunkwa munkanda.  
\v 9 Awa mpawo bamawuso nibaknodikpapila akundisunka lubo, alubo, mumyaaka makumi one bakabona nchito zyangu.  
\v 10 Aboobo zyalane eelyo telyakandibotezya pe. Ndakati, 'Bakkede kabasweeka mumyoyo yabo. Tabana kuziba nzila zyangu.'  
\v 11 Kulibiyo mbuli mbundakakonka mukunyema kwangu: 'Tabakoyonjila pe mukulykookezya kwangu.'”  
\v 12 Amuchenjele, nobakwesu, kuchitila kuti akati kenu takubi naba omwe uyooba amoyo mubi wakutasyoma, moyo uuchija kuzwa kuli Leza uupona.  
\v 13 Pesi, amusungwaazyanie abuzuba, biyo kalitegwa ngu “sunu,” kuchitila kuti kutakabi akati kenu uyoyuma moyo nkaambo ka lweeno lwachibi.  
\v 14 Nkaambo twakaba balyidilani aKkilisito, tulijisi busichaamba busimide mulinguwe kuzwa kumatalikilo kuyosika kumamanino.  
\v 15 Aatala azeezi zyakaambwa kuti, “Sunu, na mwamvwa jwi lyakwe, mutayumyi moyo yenu, mbuli mulupapi.”  
\v 16 Ngwani wakamvwa Leza mpawo wapapa? Teensi mbaabo boonse na bakazwa mu Ijipiti kabagwisigwa a Mozesi?  
\v 17 Ngwani ngwaakanyemenede kwamyaaka makumi one? Teensi mbaabo bakabisya na, aabo nbalamitunta yakawida musokwe?  
\v 18 Nkulini nkwaakakonka kuti tabakoyonjila mukulyookezya kwakwe, na kakutali kuli aabo bakatamulemeka?  
\v 19 Alimwi tuli kubwene kuti tebakakonzya pe kunjila mukulyookezya kwakwe nkaambo kakutasyoma.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Aboobo atuchenjele kuchitila kuti kutabi umwi aakati kenu uyoboneka kakachilwa kuzuzikizya chisyomezyo nchimwaka siilwa chakunjila mukulyookezya kwa Leza.  
\v 2 Nkaambo twakabuzigwa majwi mabotu mbuli mbaabede. Pesi aayo majwi taakabagwasya pe aabo bakatajatana mulusyomo abaabo bakalemeka.  
\v 3 Nkaambo swebo nitwakasyoma ndiswe tutakanjile mukulyookezya, mbuli mbakaamba kuti, “Mbuli mbundakakonka mubunyeme bwangu, tabakaoyonjila pe mukulyookezya kwangu.” Nikuba boobo, milimo yoonse njaakalenga yakamaninsigwa kumalengelo aanyika.  
\v 4 Nkaambo wakati muli bumwi busena aataka abuzuba bwamusanu atubili, “Leza wakalyookezya mubuzuba bwamusanu atubili kuzwa kumilimu yakwe yoonse,”  
\v 5 Alubo pwakati, “Tabakoyonjila mukulyookezya kwangu.”  
\v 6 Aboobo, mbulikuti kuchili mweenya wabamwi biyo kuti bakanjile mukulyookezya kwakwe, akuti nkaambo kakuti bana Izilayili biingi taakwe nibakakunjila nkaambo kakuleya milawu,  
\v 7 Leza watala alubo limbi zuba litegwa, “Sunu.” Musule lyamazuba miingi, wakaambuula kwiinda muli Devidi kuti, mbuli mbuzyakaambidwe kusanguna, “Sunu na mwalimvwa jwi lyakwe, tamuyumyi myoyo yenu.”  
\v 8 Nkaambo kansinga Joshuwa wakabapa kulyookezya, Leza wakalikunowaambuula aatala alimbi zuba.  
\v 9 Aboobo mpukuchili kulyookezya kwa Sabata kubambilidwe bantu ba Leza.  
\v 10 Nkaambo awumwi uunjila mukulyookezya kwa Leza, alakwe mwini unoli walyookezya kumilimu yakwe, mbuli Leza mbalyokezya kuli yakwe.  
\v 11 Aboobo, atuyandisye kunjila mukulyookezya ooko, kuchitila kuti kutabo uyoonjila mukutaswilila mbuli mbubakachita.  
\v 12 Nkaambo jwi lya Leza lilapona alimwi lilabosya kwiinda panga linenga mabazu aabili. Lilayasa nikuba kuyowanzaania muuya wamuntu amuuya wa Leza, antoomwe akwaanzaania moolyo aawo mpuuswaanana. Lilakonzya kuziba ziyandwa aziyeyegwa aamoyo.  
\v 13 Taakwe chakalengwa chisisidwe kunembo lya Leza. Pesi zyoonse zili salede alimwi zili aantanganana kumenso aakwe ngutweelede kulemeka  
\v 14 Aboobo, mbukunga tuli amupayizi mupati loko wakayinda mumajulu, Jesu mwana wa Leza, wakapa kuti tujatisye kulusyomo lwesu.  
\v 15 Nkaambo tatuke mupayizi muati uutakonzyi kutufwida nsoni mubutela bwesu. Pesi, tuli aawe wakanjila munzila zyoonse zyamasunko mbulindiswe, kusiya biyo kuti we takwe chibi pe.  
\v 16 Atwiinke aboobo abusichaamba kuchuuno chakwe chaluzyalo, kuchitila kuti tukatambule nsoni akujana luzyalo lwakugwasya muchiindi chapenzi.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Nkaambo awumwi mupayizi mupati, wakasalwa kuzwa mubantu, usalilwa kwiiminina bantu muzintu zya Leza, kuchitila kuti apede zipo azipayizyo zyazibi.  
\v 2 Ulakonzya kubeleka kabotu abatazi abaabo bapapide nkaambo we alakwe ulaabo butela.  
\v 3 Nkaambo kazeezi we alakwe kwelede kuti ape zipayizyo zyazibi zyakwe, mbuli mbachita kuzibi zyabantu.  
\v 4 Alimwi tachili chakwe pe kuti umwi abweze bulemu bwakwe. Uliitwa a Leza, mbuli Aaloni mbakabede.  
\v 5 Munzila njiyeeyo, alakwe Kkilisito taakwe naakalisumpula mukulichita mupayizi, Pesi, ooyo wakalikwaambuula aawe wakalikuti, “Ulimwana wangu; sunu ndaba Wuso.”  
\v 6 Kulimbuli mbukwaambidwe kulibumwi busena kutgi, “Uli mupayizi walyoonse mbuli Melukkizedeki.”  
\v 7 Muchiindi chakwe chakuba munyama, Kkilisito wakapeda nkambyo azikumbizyo ajwi pati lyakulila misozi kuli Leza, ooyo walikukonzya kumufutula kuzwa kulufu. Wakamvigwa nkaambo kakulila kwakwe.  
\v 8 Nikuba kuti wakali mwana, wakayiya kuteelela kuzintou nzyakapenzegwa kulinzizyo.  
\v 9 Wakachitwa mululami mpawo, kubantu boonse bamulemeka, wakabapa lufutuko lutaman.  
\v 10 Wakasalwa a Leza mbuli mupayizi mupati mbuli Melukkizedeki.  
\v 11 Tuli aazyiikngi zyakwaambula aatala aJesu, pesi kwayuma kupandulula nkaambo mwayuma kumizeezo yenu akukumvwa.  
\v 12 Nikuba muli eehi chiindi mwelede kuba bayiisyi, mucheelede kuba aamuntu umuyiisya ziiyandikana zya Leza amajwi aakwe. Muyanda malili peepe chakulya chisimide.  
\v 13 Nkaambo awumi unywa malili tanakomena pe mumajwi aabululami nkaambo uchili mwana mutete.  
\v 14 Pesi chakulya chisimide nchabantu baati. Aba mbaabo banga nkaamo kakukomena kwabo balalwiiyo mukumvwisisisya kwabo akwaanzaania chibi kuzwa kuchibpotu   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 Mpawo elyo atusimye matalikilo aamkani aaaJesu mpawo tuye kunembo akukomena. Tutayali lubo matalikilo azya kusanduka kuzwa kumilimu ifwide azyalusyomo muli Leza.  
\v 2 Olo matalikilo aanjisyo yazyalubbabbatizyo, buyale bwamaboko, bubuke bwabafu, alubeta lutamani.  
\v 3 Tuyochita lubo aswe echi naLeza wachizumizya.  
\v 4 Nkaambo nchiyumu kuli aabo ibakali bamunikilwa, ibalakalabila zipo zyakujulu, abo bakali basikwaaba baMuuya Uusalala,  
\v 5 mpawo akulabila ijwi bbotu lyaLeza amanguzu achiindi chiza,  
\v 6 pesi abo ibakawa - nkuyumu kubaboozya lubo kukusanduka. Kuloobu akaambo kakuti balikuligankamina lubo Mwana waLeza, mpawo akumusya lubo chaantanganana.  
\v 7 Nkambo inyiika inywa kumvula iyiwida aachiindi, akumezeka ziliimwa zilamulimu kuli abo nyika mbiyakaliminwa - eyi ninyika itambula zilongezyo zizwa kuli Leza.  
\v 8 Pesi ikuti yazyala maamvwa, amanchenya, tayigwasyi pe elyoo ili afwifwi alutuko. Mamanino ayo alimukutentwa.  
\v 9 Pesi twakakomenenwa kuzintu zili mbubombubo aatala anduwe, nobayandwa, zintu zilangene alufutuko, nikuba kuto twaamba oobu.  
\v 10 Nkaambo Leza takwe lubazu. Takoyoluba mulimu wako aluyamdo nduwakatondeezya kuzina lyakwe, nkaambo wakagwasya basalali bakwe, a lino uchibagwasya.  
\v 11 Tuli achiyandisyo kapati kuti awumwi akati kanu akatondezye bukozu bukozyene kumamanino, kuti bulangizi bwanu bube bwanchonzyo.  
\v 12 Eechi nkokuti mutakabi bakand, pesi batobelezyi babaabo kwindila mulusyomo abulindizi bakone zisyomezyo.  
\v 13 Nkaambo Leza naakachita chisyomezyo kuli Abbulamu, wakalikonkezya mwini, mukuti taali kanookonkezya kuli umwi mupati kampatila.  
\v 14 Wakati “ Chonzyo ndiyokulongezya a kukomezya myeelwe yako.”  
\v 15 Munzila eeyi, Abbulamu wakachijana echo nchakasyomezegwa musule abulindizi buzulide.  
\v 16 NKaambo bantu balakonkezya kuli umwi mupati kwinda lwabo beni. Kumamanino a twaambo twabo, achizuminano chiyoba mbuli chizuzikizyo.  
\v 17 Elyo Leza nakasala kutondeezya chilaantanganana kuli basimulya lukono lwazisyomezyo kutasanduka kwabube bwakwe, wakachibikila chizuminano.  
\v 18 Wakachita obu kuti kuzintu zibili zitasandululwi - kuli eecho chitakonzeki kuti Leza abeje - iswe, nitwakachijila kumayubilo, tuyooba akusungwazigwa kupati mukujatisya changuzu bulangizi bubikidwe kunembo lyesu.  
\v 19 Tulabulangizi obu mbuli chikwabilizyo chesu a chisimyo chitazunganisigwi chamuuya, bulangizi obo mubusena bwamukatikati kusule a chisitikizyo, oko  
\v 20 Jesu, wakeendakunembo lyesu, nkwakanjilila mubusena obo akambo kesu. Elyo wakaba mupayizi mupati kwakutamani musule amalayilile aMelikizedeki.   
\c 7  
\p
\v 1 Wakali ooyu Melekizedeki mwami wakuSalemu, mupayizi waLeza usumpukide wakaswanana aAbbulamu kaboola kuzwa kwakali kufundwa baami mpawo wakamulongezya.  
\v 2 Nkulinguwe oko Abbulamu nkwakapa chibeela chaachakummi chazyonse. Lutanzi kupandulwa kwazina lyakwe chaamba kuuti “mwaami wabululami,” alimwi utegwa “mwami wakuSalemu,” chamba kuti “mwami walumuno.”  
\v 3 Takwe wisi, takwe banyina, takwe basikale, katakwe nikuba kutalika kwamazuba anikuba kwabuumi. Nikuba oobo, uyiminide mwana waLeza, nkambo unolimupayizi kwalyonse.  
\v 4 Bona bupati kuloyu mwalumi wachiindi Abbulamu ngwakapa chipanzi chakkumi kuzintu nzyakatola munkondo.  
\v 5 Izyalane lya Levi eelyo litambula mulimu wabupayizi balamalayilile kwinda mumulawu kuti batole zyachakkumi, kubantu nkuukuti chizwa kuli babunyina nikuba kuti ambabo nizyalane lizwa kuliAbbulamu.  
\v 6 Pesi Melekizedeki, ulazyalane elyo lyakatali lyabo lyakatambula chakkumi kuzwa kuli mbabo, wakatambula zyakkumi kuzwa kuli Abbulamu akumulongezya, oyo wakali azisyomezyo.  
\v 7 Takwe zikazyana akuti muntu munini ulongezegwa amupati.  
\v 8 Mulaya makkani muntu wanyama ulatambula chakkumi, pesi mumakani aya kulibukamboni bwakuti unochipona.  
\v 9 Mpawo, kwinda munzila yakwambula, muLevi ooyo wakali kutambula chakkumi, alakwe wakali kugwisya chakkumi kwinda kuli Abbulamu,  
\v 10 nkaambo Levi wakali mumubili wazyalane awo Melekizedeki nakaswanana aAbbulamu.  
\v 11 Lino anoli bululami bwakali konzekene kwindila mubupayizi bwabu Levi (aawo muunsi azezi bantu bakatambula mulawo), ninzi eecho chakali kuyandikana kunembo eecho chinoli chakalelede kubawo kuti kube umbi mupayizi kuti abewo kunembo mubube bwa Melekizedeki, mpawo kitatolegwi kuti ibe kunembo kuliAaloni?  
\v 12 Mpawo kuti bupayizyo bwasandulwa, mulawo awulawo uyelede kuti wasandulwa.  
\v 13 Ooyo umwi wambwa azeezi zintu ngwawumbi musyobo, utakwe umwi wakali wabelekela achipayililo.  
\v 14 Lino zilantanganana kuti eezi zizwa kuli Juda oko Mwami nkwakazyalilwa, musyobo Mozesi ngwakwakatamba atala abupayizi.  
\v 15 Ezyo nzitwamba zimvwikka loko zyakuti anoli umwi mupayizi wabuka muchikozya chaMelekizedeki.  
\v 16 Tewakalanagene loko pe aziyandikana amulawu wanyama kukuba muapayizi, pesi wo wali atala amanguzu abuumi butamani.  
\v 17 Nkambo magwalo ababukamboni anguwe: “Ulimupayizi kwalyoonse kwinda mumabmbe aMelikizedeki.”  
\v 18 Tazyambi kuti ayo malayilile achindi akabikwa kumbi kumbali akaambo alikumpeme akubula mulimu.  
\v 19 Nkaambo mulawo takwe nchwakachita chiluleme - pesi alubo bulangizi balimbubo bwakazibisigwa kwinda nituswena kuliLeza.  
\v 20 Chamba kuti tezyakali achikonke pe! Bamwi bakaba bapayizi kabatakwe chikonke pe.  
\v 21 Pesi wakaba mupayizi kwinda muchikonke nchaakatola kulumwi ooyo wakati kulinguwe, “Mwaami wakakonka alubo taakwe nazosanduka pe muzezo wakwe: Ulimupayizi kwalyoonse.”  
\v 22 Alubo kuli eechiJesu wakapa chisinizyo chachizuminano chilimbubo.  
\v 23 Bapayizi bataanzi bakali biingi mumweelwe, mbulu kuti lufu lwakabakachizya kuti bayimkilile nkabali munganda yamulimu.  
\v 24 Pesi akambo kakuti Jesu ulapona kwalyonse, ulabupayizi bwalyoonse.  
\v 25 Mpawo ulakonzya lubo kufutula chakumanina basikila Leza kwinda mulinguwe nkaambo choonse chiindi uponena kubakombela.  
\v 26 Nkaambo nochoonzyo chaakelela kuti tuube amupayizi mupati, ooyo usalala, utakwe chiibi, uwanzanisigilwe kuzya kuli basizibi akusumpulwa ataala lyamajulu.  
\v 27 Ooyo utayandi, uatali mbuli bapayizi balaajula, kuti ape zipayizyo zyabuzu abuza, kutaangu chazibi zyakwe, mpawo zyazibi zyabantu. Nakachita eechi lumwi kuli boonse nakalipeda.  
\v 28 Nkambo mulawu upa bapayizi kumuntu ulabukompami. Pesi ijwi lyachi chikonke, eelyo lyakaza kunembo amulawu, lyakapa mwana, ooyo wakasalazigwa kwalyoonse.   
\c 8  
\p
\v 1 Lino kaambo nkitulikwaamba: Tulijisi mupayizi mupati wakkala aansi kuluboko lwachilisyo lwachuuno chabulemu cha Singuzu zsyoonse mumajulu.  
\v 2 Mubeleki mubusena busalala, idyuumba lya choonzyo, elyo Mwami pepe muntu, ndyakayala.  
\v 3 Woonse mupayizi ulasalwa kuti ape zipo antjkoomwe azituuzyo. Lino kulayandikana kuba achimwi chakupa.  
\v 4 Lino koonzinga Jesu uli aanyika, tewalikunoba mupayizi kale pe, mbulikuthi kuli aabo bapa zipo kwiinda mumu lawu.  
\v 5 Babeleka kabatobelezya alimwi munzinzimwa wazintu zyakujulu. Kuli biyo mbuli Mozesi mbaka chenjezegwa a Leza naakali waamba kuyaka dyumba: Leza wakaamba kuti, “Langa kuti uchite zyoonse mbuli mumabambe aayo ngwaakatondezegwa aatala lyachilundu.”  
\v 6 Pesi lino Jesu watambulwa mumbungano ilimbubo, mbuli mbali simwiima akati kachizuminano chilimbubo eecho chichita zisyomezyo zilimbubo.  
\v 7 Kuti eechiya chizuminano chakutanguna teechakali abubi, taakwe nikwalikuno chitwa chimbi chizuminano.  
\v 8 Elyo Leza nkalikunoonga wajana bubi abantu, wakalikwaamba kuthi, “Amubone mazuba ayobuza, mbwaamba Mwami - elyo nindiyo chita chizuminano chipya ang'anda ya Izilayeli alimwi ang'anda ya Juda.  
\v 9 Takukwe nikuyoba mbuli chizuminano nchindakachitide abasikale benu mubuzuba mbundakabajata akuboko kubagwisya mu Ijipiti. Nkaambno tebakeenda muchizuminano changu, alimwi ndakabatakata - mbawamba Mwami.  
\v 10 Nkaambo eechi nche chizuminano nchindiyochita ang'anda ya Izilayeli musule lyamazuba ayo - mbawamba Mwami. Ndiyobikka milawu yangu mumizeezo yabo, alimwi ndiyoyi lemba mumykoyo yabo. Ndiyoba Leza wabo alimwi bayoba bantu bangu  
\v 11 Tabakoykooyiisya basimabambanwa babo na bana bakwaabo kabati, 'Ziba Mwami.' Nkaambo boonse bayondiziba], kuzwa kumuniini kuyoosika kumupati wabo.  
\v 12 Nkaambo ndiyooba aluzyalo kuchito zyabo zyakutalulama, alimwi nsikoyoziyeeya lubo pe zibi zyabo.”  
\v 13 Mukwiita chizuminano echi kuti, “chipya,” wakachita chizuminano chakusanguna chibe chikulukulu. Alimwi eecho chaba chachiindi alimwi kachili chi kulukulu chaba afwiifwi kuti chiinde.   
\c 9  
\p
\v 1 Lino nikuba chizuminano chitanzi chakalijisi milawo atala akukukomba abusena bwachiyubilo chaansi.  
\v 2 Nkaambo dumba lyakukombela mwakalichibikilo chalambe atebuli, achinkwa chabuliwo bwakwe, bwakali kuyitwa kuti busena busalala.  
\v 3 Musule adembo lyachibili kwakali limbi dumba lyakukombela, buitwa kuti busena busalalisya.  
\v 4 Lyakali angolide yachipayililo yatununkilizyo. Alimwi ilabhokesi bwachizuminano, yakazililwidwe angolide koonse, koonse. Mukati mwakali nkomesi yangolide yakajisi chitegwa maana, musako waAloni wakalinonga wasyukila aya mabbwe akalembedwe majwi achizuminano.  
\v 5 Atala abhokesi lyachizuminano, bangelo bajisi bulemu bakavumbide chivunisyo, echo chitutakonzyi kwambula atala anchicho mubunike.  
\v 6 Nizyakamana kubambwa ezi zintu bapayizi choonse chiindi bakalikunjilila mung'andu yakunze ya dumba lyakukombela kuti bakachite milimu yabo.  
\v 7 Pesi mupayizi mupati luzutu wakanonga wanjila mung'anda yakunze ya dumba lyakukombela kuti bakachite milimu yabo.  
\v 8 Muuya usalalala wakatondezya kuti na dumba taanzi kalichimvwi mukati kanzila yabusena busalalisya butaboneki.  
\v 9 Echi chakulitondezya muchindi echo zyonse ziipo azipayililo ezyo lino zilikupegwa tazichiti kusalazya bakombi amamvwido.  
\v 10 Balalangilila kupela chakulya akunywa azyakutula zisiyene - siyene zyakusamba, malayilile amibili kusiika chiindi chabubambululwe bupya.  
\v 11 Kilisito nakasika mbuli muapayizi mupati wazintu zibotu zyaksika wakeenda mukati kadumba lyakukombela pati lisalalisya litesi lyakabumbwa amaanza abantu chimwi kachitali chanyika eyi yakalengwa.  
\v 12 Tekwakali kwabulowa bwampongo abwang'ombe, pesi abulowa bwakwe obo bwakanjilila mubusena busalalisya kamwi kwalyoonse akujana akukwabilila kwaununuko lwenu lutamani.  
\v 13 Kansinga bulowa bwampongo abaasune, akusansayilwa kwadyota kulibabo bakalisofwazya zyakaba salazya kukusanzigwa kwamibili yabo,  
\v 14 buyoba byeni bulowa bwaKkilisito, ngwani mukwiinda mumuya uusalala utamani wakalipeda lwakwe mwiini kutakwe kampenda kuli Leza, kuto asalazye kubisya kwesu kuzwa kumilimu ifwide kuti babelekele Leza upona?  
\v 15 Akambo kabobu ngusikwima akati wachizuminano chipya. Ezi zilimbulikuti kuzwa kuchindi lufu nilwakabweza busena mulwangunuko kulibabo bali ansi achizuminano chitanzi kuzwa kuzibi zyabo, abo bayitwa kuti bayojana chisyomezyo chitamani chalukono.  
\v 16 Awo ali chiyandisyo, lufu lwamuntu wakuluchita uyoluzuzikizya.  
\v 17 Nkaambo kuyanda kubabiyo nakwakaba lufu, nkaambo takwe lukakatizya kuliyoyo wakalubumba uchipona.  
\v 18 Pesi alacho chizuminano chitanzi chakabambwa kachitakwe bulowa.  
\v 19 Kufumbwa Mozesi wakalikupa lulayililo luli mumulawu kubantu kubantu boonse, wakabweza bulowa bwabana bang'ombe ampongo, ameenda, buluba busalala, amichelo yahisopi akubusansila zyoonse ibhuku abantu boonse.  
\v 20 Wakati, “ Obu mbulowa bwachizuminano echo Leza nchakamulayilila.”  
\v 21 Alubo wakasansila bulowa mu dumba lyachikombelo azyoonse zibikilo zyakalikubelesya mumilimu.  
\v 22 Mbuli kumulawo zyoonse zyakasalazigwa abulowa kakutali kutika kwabulowa takwe lulekelelo.  
\v 23 Nkinkakako nchikwakalikabotu kuti, zikozyanyo zyazintu zyakujulu kuti zisalazigwe azipayizyo zyabanyama aba. Aboobo, zintu zyakujulu lwazyo zyakalelede kusalazigwa azipayizyo zilikabotu.  
\v 24 Nkaambo Kkilisito takanjila mubusena busalalisya bwakachitwa amaboko, kachili chikozyano chawumwi wakasimpe. Pesi wakanjilwa kujulu lini kuti alibonye mubuliwo bwaLeza mulindiswe.  
\v 25 Takayinka oko kuti akalipe mwini muzintu zyiingi, mbuli mbuwakachita mupayizi mupati, unjila mubusena busalalisaya bwamunyaka amunyaka abulowa bwawumwi.  
\v 26 Nikuli ako nkikaambo, mpawo ulelede kufwaba muzintu zyiingo kuzwa kuntalisyo yanyika. Pesi lino wasika chantanganana kumamanino azyiindi kuzogwisya kulibali azibi kulipayizya kwakwe mwini.  
\v 27 Mbuli muntu bwakasalwa kuti afwe kamwi, alimwi kuzwawo kuyosika lubeta.  
\v 28 Alubo, Kkilisito wakapedwa lumwi kuti agwisye zibi zyabiingi, alimwi uzoboneka lwabili, kuti atazobi abwendelezi azibi, pesi lufutuko kulibabo bamulindilide.   
\c 10  
\p
\v 1 Nkaambo mulawu mwenzwide bikupayilwayo wazikntu zibotu zichiza, kawutali chiimo loko pe chazintu eezi. Aabo baza kuli Leza tabakonzyi pe kululamikwa anzizyo zipayizyo nzibaswini kabapayila munyaka amunyaka.  
\v 2 Mulikumwi kwaamba konzo zipayizyo tezyaka yimikizigwa? Na kakuli boobo, na kazili zyasalazigwa zyamanina aatu, basykomi teensi balikunoba kabaziba zibi pe.  
\v 3 Pesi muzipayizyo eezi kuli kuyeezegwa kwazibi amunyaka amunyaka.  
\v 4 Nkaambo tazichiti pe kuti bulowa bwaba pule bang'ombe ampongo bumane milandu.  
\v 5 Lino Kkilisito naakasika munyika, wakati, “Zipayizyho azipo tenzizyo nzwakayandisisya pe. Pesi, wakali mubili ngumwakandibambila.  
\v 6 Kazitali muzipayizyho zitentedwe na zipayizyo zyazibi nzimwakabotelwa kulinzizyo.  
\v 7 Mpawo ndakati, 'Langa, ndasika, mbuli mukulembedwe atala andime mumalembe, chita kuyanda kwako.'”  
\v 8 Kakutanguna wakati, “Teensi zipayizyo pe, na zipo, niziba zyoonse zipayizyo zyakuumpa, mna zipayizyo zyazibi nzimwakalikuyanda. Na kubotelwa mulinzizyo.” Eezi nzezipayizyo zipegwa kwiinda mumulawu.  
\v 9 Mpawo wakati, “Langa mpawa ndili wano kuti ndichite lkuyanda kwenu.” Wakagwisya mabelekelo mataanzi kuti asangune mabelekelo aabili.  
\v 10 Munzila eeyi, twakasalazigwa kwiinda mukupayilwa kwamubili wa Jesu Kkilisitu mpawo kwamanina aatu.  
\v 11 Kulilimwi bbazu, buzuba abuzuba, awumwi mupayizi ulayimikila kubelekela Leza. Ukkede kapayila zipayizyo nzizyo nzizyo, nikuba tazikwe nizisalazya zibi pe.  
\v 12 Kúli limwi bbazu, Kkilisito wakapayila chipayizyo chomwe kwa lyoonse, wakakkala ansi kululyo lwa Leza.  
\v 13 Ulilindide mane basinkondonyina bakachitwe chilyatilizyo chamawulu aakwe.  
\v 14 Nkaambo achipayizyo chomwe wakalulamika aabo balikusalazigwa.  
\v 15 Alimwi Muuya Uusalala ulatwaambilila kulindiswe. Nkaambno usanguna kati,  
\v 16 “Eechi nchechizuminano nchesikachite aabo musule lyawayo mazuba ayo, mbawamba Mwami. Ndiyobikka milawu yangu mumyoyo akwilemba mumizeezo yabo  
\v 17 Taakwe nesikaziyeeye lubo pe zibi zyabo.”  
\v 18 Lino aawo ali kulekelelwa kwabaaba, taachikwe nikucheelede zipayizyo zyazibi pe.  
\v 19 Aboobo, bana bakwesu, twaba achaamba chakunjila mubusena busalalisya nkaambo kabulowa bwa Jesu.  
\v 20 Njenzila mpya yakupomna njatujulila kwiinda mudyembo nkukwaambo kuti mubili wakwe.  
\v 21 Nkaambo tujis mupayizi mupati kampatila wang'anda ya Leza,  
\v 22 atunjile amyooyo yachoonzyo amulusyomo luzwide, moyo yesu kiisaledekuzwa kumizeezo amibili yesu kisanzizigwe amaanzi aaslala.  
\v 23 Alukbo ngatujatisye katutazungani kubulangizi mbutulingulula, nkaambo ooyo wakasyomezya ulisyomekede.  
\v 24 Tuyeesesye mbutunga tulasungwaazyania umwi awumi mumilimu yaluyando.  
\v 25 Tutanoleki kuswaanana, mbuli mbubakaleka bamwi. Pesoi agtusungwaazyanie umwi awumwi mukuvula akwiinkila kunembo mbuli mbumukubwene kuti buzuba bwaba afwiifwi.  
\v 26 Kuti na twachita chibi achaali musule akutambula busongo akasimpe, chipayizyo chazibi tachichiwo pe.  
\v 27 Pele kwasyaala biyo kubetekwa kuyoosya, abukali bwamulilo buyotenta basinkondonyina ba Leza.  
\v 28 Kufumbwa uukaka mulawu wa Mozesi ulafwa katausilwi pe kakuli bakamboni babili na nbatatu.  
\v 29 Muyeeya kuti nga chilatana aali chisubulo chipegwa ooyo wakaba kunsi lyamawulu aMwana wa Leza, oyo wakabweza bulowa bwachizuminano mbuli butasalede, - bulowa bulimbubo bwakamululamika - mpawo wakatukila Muuya waluzyalo?  
\v 30 Nkaambo tulimuzi wakati, “Kukolotya nkukwangu; ndiyobbadala.” Alubo, Mwami uyobeteka bantu bakwe.”  
\v 31 Nchintu chiyoosya kuwida mumaboko a Leza uupona.  
\v 32 Pesi aukayeeye mazuba akusanguna nimwakajana mumuni, kuti mwakasima biyeni mukulwana amukoomba.  
\v 33 Mwakaba akusampawoulwa aluundu akupenzegwa, alimwi mwakali kwaabilana abaabo bamwi bakiinda mubusampawuzi amapenzi aya.  
\v 34 Nkaambo mwakali aluse kuli aabo bakangidwe alimwi mwakali kutambula amoyo omwe kunyanzigwa zintu zyenu. Mwakalizi lwanu kuti mwakalizi kuti mulijis lubono lutamani.  
\v 35 Aboobo tamusowi chaamba chenu, chijyoomweetela mpindu mpati.  
\v 36 Nkaambo muyanda kuba akukakatila, kuchitila kuti mukatambule eezyo Leza nzyakamusyhomezya, kamuli mwachita luyando lwakwe.  
\v 37 “Nkaambo muchiindi chifwiifwi chimboola, ooyo uzabuza ulasika alimwi tachedwi pe.  
\v 38 Mululami wangu uyoopona alusyomo. Naayoowa, nsikoyoomubotelwa pe.”  
\v 39 Pesi tatuli babaabo bawa pe kababweeda kukunyonyoonwa. Pesi, tuli bamwi babaabo bajisi lusyomo lwakubamba myuuya yesu.   
\c 11  
\p
\v 1 Lino lusyomo nkuba akasimpe kazintu zilangilidwe alimwi abwini bwazintu zitaboneko.  
\v 2 Aboobo nkaambo kacheechi basikale bakatambulika nkaambo kalusyomo lwabo.  
\v 3 Kwiinda mulusyomo tumvwisisya kuti nyika yakalengwa akulayilila kwaLez, kutondezya kuti iziboneka tezyakalengwa kuzwa kuzintu zyakali kuboneka.  
\v 4 Nkaambo kalusyomo Abbelu wakapa Leza chipayizyo chibotu kwiinda cha Keyini, nkakasunkwa aacho kukuba mululami alimwi Leza wakambula kabotu aatala anguwe nkaambo kazipayizyo zyakwe, alimwi kwiinda mulusyomo Abbelu uchambuula nikuba kuti ulifwide.  
\v 5 Nkaambo kalusyomo Inoki wakatolwa biyo kujulu katabwene lufu. “Taakajanika nkaambo Leza wakamubweza.” Awo katana tolw, kwakaba bukmaboni bwakuti wakali wabotezya Leza.  
\v 6 Lino uti kakutakwe lusyomo tazikonzeki pe kumubotezya. Nkaambo chileelede kuti kufumbwa uuza kuliLeza welede kusyoma kuti mpali alimwi mulumbuli wababo bamuyandula.  
\v 7 Ndusyomo lwakachita kuti Nowa, nakali wapegwa mulumbe wakujulu aatala azintu zikatalina boneka mukuba abulemu buli abunaLeza wakayaka bwaato ktui afutule mpuli yakwe. Mukuchita oobu wakiipa mulandu nyika eelyo wakaba simulyazina wabululami buza alusyomo.  
\v 8 Ndusyomo lwakachita kuti Abbulamu, nakiitwa wakateelela wiinka kubusena, oobo mbwakelede kutambula mbuuli lukono. Wakazwa wiinka, katanzi nkwaali kuya.  
\v 9 Ndusyomo lwakachita kuti akale munyika yechisyomezyo mbuli muzwa kule. Wakakala mumatente antoomwe aAyizeki aJekkobbu, basimulyazinanyina kuchisyomezyo chomwe biyo.  
\v 10 Nkaambo wakali kulangilila kugunzi lilaantalisyo mubambi amuyaki wazyo kali nguLeza.  
\v 11 Mulusyomo - alimwi Sala lwakwe wakali ngomwa wakatambula kukonzya kumita mwana mubuchembele bwakwe, mukubona kasyomekede oyo wakapa chisyomezyo. Kulimubuzyo wakutii lwakali lusyomo lwaAbbulahamu na kana lwaSala lwakali kuboneka awa. Mulusyomo Sala, nikuba kuti wakali wachembala, wakatambula nguzu zyakuzyala mwana, nkaambo wakabona kasyomekede oyo wakapa chisyomezyo.  
\v 12 Aboobo kuzwa kumwalumi oyu omwe alimwiwakali wamba kufwa - kwakazyalwa bana bingi mbuuli nyenyeezi zya julu alimwi batabaliki mbuuli luseese lwakumbali alwizi.  
\v 13 Chakali mulusyomo kuti boons aaba bakafwa kabatatambwide zisyomezyo. Muchiindi eecho, nibaka ibona akuzi juzya kazili kule, bakazumina kuti bakali banasinakooma munyika.  
\v 14 Kuli aabo baamba zintu ziliboobu babika antaanganana kuti bayandula nyika yakukala.  
\v 15 Nikwali kuti bakali kuyeeya nyika njibakazwa kulinjiyo bali kunoowujana mweenya wakubweeda.  
\v 16 Pesi mbuuli mbuzibede bayndula nyika mbotu kwiinda, nkokuti, yakujulu. Aboobo Leza takwe nsoni akwambwa kuti nguLeza wabo, mbuli kuti wakaba bambila muunzi.  
\v 17 Nguwakali mwana wakwe omwe biyo ngwakapedekezy, ooyo wakatambula zisyomezyo.  
\v 18 Ezi zyakambilwa Abbulahamu, “mazyalane aako ayowuzikwa kwindila muli Ayizeki”  
\v 19 Abbulahamu wakayeeya kuti Leza wakalikukonzya kumubusya Ayizeki kuzwa kubafu, alimwi kwaambisya mumaboneno aakwe wakamutambulalubo kuzwa kulimbabo.  
\v 20 Ayizeki wakalongezya Jekkobbu aIsawu kwindilila mulusyomo aatala azintu zyakachiyobuza.  
\v 21 Kwindila mulusyomo Jakkobbu naakaba afwiifwi akufwa wakalongezya banabaJOzefu balombe umwi awumwi. Jekkobbu wakakomba, kakoteme aamufunko wakwe.  
\v 22 Kwindila mulusyomo Jozef, mamanino aakwe naakab aafwifwi, wakambuula atala akulonga kwabana ba - Isilayeli kuzwa ku - Igipite alimwi wakabalayilila aatala amafuwa akwe.  
\v 23 Kwakalikwindila mulusymo, Mozesi naakazyala, wakasiswa kwamyeezi yotatwe abazyali bakwe nkaambo bakabona kuti mwana mubotu. Tabayowede kulayilila kwamwami.  
\v 24 Kwakkali kwiindila mulusyomo kuti Mozesi, naakakomena wakakkaka kwambwa kuti mwana waFalo.  
\v 25 Wakasala kupenzegwa antoomwe abantu baLeza kwiinda kulibotzya abunone bwachibi chindi chinini.  
\v 26 Wakayeya kuti kusampulwa kwakutobela Kkilisito bwakali buvubi bupati kwiinda buvubi bwaIgipita. Nkaambo menso aakwe wakaabikide kubulumbu bwakwe.  
\v 27 Mulusyomo Mozesi wakazwa Igipita. Takwe nakayoowa bukkali bwaMwaam. Takwe nakayowa bukkali bwaMwaam, nkaambo wakakalatila aanga wakali mubwene ooyo uutabonwi.  
\v 28 Alusyomo wakabamba Pasika akusansilwa kwabulowa, kuchitila kuti sikujaya bana bataanzi atagumi bana babana-Izilayeli balombe batanzi.  
\v 29 Alusyomo bakiinda mu; wizi lwamatete mbuli kwiinda aanyika njumu. Awobana-Igipita nibakayanda kuchita oobo bakamenwa.  
\v 30 Alusyomo bulambo bwakuJelikko bwakakkolomoka musule akuzyungulukwa kwamazuba alimusanu abili.  
\v 31 Zyakachitika mulusyomo kuti sibwaamu taakafwa pe antoomwe abasikutaswilila, nkaambo wakatambula basikutwela muluumuno.  
\v 32 Ninzi chimwi nchekonzya kwaamba? Ichiindi nsikoba aacho kuti ngambuule zyaGidiyoni, Bbalakki, Samisoni, Jefutati, Devidi, Samiyeli alimwi atala abasinsimi.  
\v 33 Kwakali kwindila mulusyomo kuti bakazunda zisi, bendelezya, bululami, alimwi bakatambula zisyomezyo. Bakajala milomo yabalavu,  
\v 34 akuzima nguzu zyamililo, bakaloboka kuyaswa asumu, bakaponesegwa kumalwazi bakaba basinguzu munkondo, akuzunda basilumamba bamazwa kule.  
\v 35 Banakazi bakatambula bafu babo abubuke. Bamwi bakoomba akufwabisigwa, kabatatambuli kwangununwa kuchitila kuti bajane bubuke bubotu kwiinda.  
\v 36 Bamwi bakatambula kunyansigwa aunabbwa, alimwi amaketaniakubikwa muntolongo.  
\v 37 Bakatululwa mabbwe. Bakkandulwa aakati. Bakajigwa asumu. Bakapwenta kabazwete zikumba zyambelele azyempongo. Bakali mubuchete, akudyamizigwa, kabtajatwi oobotu.  
\v 38 Nyika teyakabapa bulemu Lyoonse bakali bakalikupwenta munkanda amuzilundu amumapako munyika.  
\v 39 Nikuba kuti boonse bantu aaba bakalitambwidwe aLeza nkaambo kalusyomo lwabo, taakwe nibakachitambula chisyomezyo.  
\v 40 Leza wakatubambila chimwi chintu chibotu kwiinda, kuchitila kuti kuboneke aanoli tetwaliwo tebali kunoomaninizigwa pe.   
\c 12  
\p
\v 1 Mbukuliboobo, mbulikuti yuzyungulukdwe joba paiti lyabakamboni, atubikke kumbali kulemenwa koonse antoomwe aibi zyoonse. Atube amoyo mulamfu mukuchijaana mujiizyanio ooyu wambikkwa kunembo lyesu.  
\v 2 Atuswiilile Jesu, we ngomutaliko amumaninizyi walusyomo. Nkaambo lukondo lwakabikkwa kunembo lyakwe, wakalipeda kuchiingan, nikuba chakalikupa mawuse, mpawo wakakukkala kululyo lwachuuno chabulemu cha Leza.  
\v 3 Aboobo amumuyeye, ooyo wakatola chiimo chili boobo kuli basizibi chiteendelani aguwe, kuchihtila kuti tamubi abutela mumyoyo yanu.  
\v 4 Taakwe nimwalina lwana achibi kuyosika kubulowa.  
\v 5 Alimwi mwakaluba kusungwaazigwa kumwaambila kuti inywe mbuli bana balombe: “Mwanangu, utayeeyi kuti milawu ya Mwami myuuba, na kuba abutela awo nowambilwa atala akuchita chibi anguwe.  
\v 6 Nkaambo Mwami ulapa malayilile kuli woonse muntu ngwayanda alimwi ulasubula mwana woonse ngwatambula.  
\v 7 Sima mukuenzegwa akulayigwa. Leza ubeleka andinywe mbuli bana. Ulabanzi ooyo mwana uula wisi utamu layi?  
\v 8 Pesi kuti kotakwe buntu, obo bantu boonse mbubaabana, ulimwana uutatambuliki alimwi toyelede pe kuba mwana wakwe.  
\v 9 Kuyakukunembo, twakalijisi bama taata bamunyama mbuli basikiutulayilila, alimwi twakabalemeka. Tatweelede na aboobo kuti tulemeke Wisi wa myuuya kuti tupone?  
\v 10 Nkaambo kulilimwi bbazu, bama taata besu bakatulayilila kwamazuba mache mbuli mbubakalikubona kazyeelede kulimbabo. Pesi kulilimwi bbazu leza uchita oobo kuti zitubotele kuchitila kuti tukaabaane aawe mubusalali.  
\v 11 Taakwe kulayililwa kuboneka kakubotela muntu muli eecho chiindi pesi kulachisa. Pesi muchiindi chiboola kuleta muchelo waluumuno mubululami kuli aabo bakalayililwa.  
\v 12 Aboobo simya maboko aako aayo asiminina aansi mazwi aako.  
\v 13 Panga nzila ziluleme zyamawulu aako, kuchitila kuti eezyo zilemene tazikoyookachilwa pesi ziyoponesegwa.  
\v 14 Amuyanduule luumuno abamwi boonse, antoomwe abusalali nkaambo iuutakwe busalali taakwe nayoomubona Mwami.  
\v 15 Amuchenjele kuti kuti takubi ubula luzyalo lwa Leza, alimwi takubi nuuba muyanda wakunyema uunga ulayeta kutamvwanana, kuchitila kuti biingi tababi kababisigwa ankuko.  
\v 16 Amuchenjele kuti takubi zyakunjila munobo zitaluleme na kuba muntu utaluleme mbuli Isawu, ooyo wakawuzya bupati bwakwe nkaambo kakulya.  
\v 17 Nkaambo mulizi kuti musule lyazezyo, naakazoyanda kutola chilongezyo, taakatambulika pe, nkaambo wakabula mweenya wakusanduka, nikunba kuti waka chiyanduula amisozi.  
\v 18 Nkaambo teensi mwaza kuchilundu chikonzeka kugumwa, chilundu chaulilo uuyaka, mudima, kutaboneka a guwo pati.  
\v 19 Teensi mwaza kuzolizya nyeele, na kujwi lyaambula majwi basikumvwa kabatamwi niliba limbi jwi lyaambuulwa kulimbabo.  
\v 20 Nkaambo tabakonzyi kuzikalilila eezyo nzibalayililwa: “Namnsya nuuba munyama waguma chilundu welede kutululwa mabwe.”  
\v 21 Chakalikuyoosya loko echi chakabonwa a Mozesi awo naakati, “Ndilikuyoowa alimwi ndilikukankama.”  
\v 22 Pesi mwasika kuchilundu cha Zayoni akudolopo lya Leza upona, Jelusalemu lyakujulu, akumakumi azyuulu zyabangelo zili kupobola.  
\v 23 Mwasika kumbungano yamwana wabubele, ooyo wakalembwa kujulu. Mwasika kuli Leza, Mubetesi waboomnse, akumyuuya yabaluleme bakalulamikwa.  
\v 24 Alimwi mwasika kuli Jesu, simwiima aakati wachizuminano chipya, akubulowa bwakasamnsiilwa bwaambula zilimbubo kwiinda bulowa bwa Abela.  
\v 25 Amubone kuti tamumukasyi ooyo uulikwaambula. Nkaambo kaansinga tebakafutuka nibakachija ooyo wakabalayilila aanyika, nkuche kuti tufuke na twachija ooyo ulikutulayilila kuzwa kujulu.  
\v 26 Mulichimwi chiindi, jwi lyakwe lyakateketesya nyika. Pesi lino wasyomezya wati, “Ilubo, nsikozoteketya nyika ayilike pe, pesi amajulu woonse.”  
\v 27 Aya majwi, “Chimbi lubo chiindi,” kwaamba kugwisya eezyo zintu zikonzya kuteketesegwa, kwaamba kuti, zintu zyakalengwa, kuchitila kuti zintu zitakonzeki kuteketesegwa zichaale.  
\v 28 Aboobo, kutambula bwami butakonzyi kuteketesegwa, atulumbe, amuleyi nzila tumukombe Leza mubulemu bupati akuyoowa.  
\v 29 Nkaambo Leza wesu mulilo uyaka akutenta.   
\c 13  
\p
\v 1 Aamulekke Luyando lwabunyina lwinkilile anembo.  
\v 2 Mutalubi kujata akabotu beenzu. Mukwindila kulechi, bamwi bakajata kabotu ibangelo kabatazi pe.  
\v 3 Kamuyeya ibangidwe mbuli kuthi mwangidwe aamwi ambabo. Kamubayeya aaba batajiswi kabotu muli mulimubili omwe.  
\v 4 Aamuleke makwatano alemekwe kuliboonse, alimwi buulo bwamakwatano abusalale, nkambo leza uyobeteka abo ibayanda malalano abasimamambe.  
\v 5 Machitilo anu atabi akuyanda mali. Amukutisikane kuzinini nzimulazyo. Nkambo Leza lwakwe wakamba kuti,”Sikoyomuleka pe, nanka kumusiya.”  
\v 6 Atukutisikane tukabe abusichamba mukwamba, “Mwami ngomugwasyi wangu; nsikoyoyowa pe. Ino muntu ulandichitanzi?  
\v 7 Kamuyeeya bazuluzi ibanu, kulabo bakamba aabo bakamwambila jwi lyaLeza, Alimwi kamwibalukwa impindu zyabweende bwabo. Kamutobelzye lusyomo lwabo.  
\v 8 Jesu Kkilisito nguwe wajilo, sunu mane kukabe kutamani.  
\v 9 Mutenwi anjisyo nzimutazi zyamusyobomusyobo. Nkambo nchibotu kuti Moyo usisimisigwe aluzyalo pe- pe azyakulya. eezyo zitagwasyi aabo benda anzizyo.  
\v 10 Tulijisi chipayililo chizwa kulabo ibabeleka muDumba lyakukkombela eelyo tabakwe cheelelo chakulya.  
\v 11 Nkambo bulowa bwabwanyama bwakafwida zibi bwaketwa abapayizi ibapati mukati kenganda isalala, muchindi echo mibili yabo yakatentwa anze mpubakakede.  
\v 12 Eelyo Jesu alakwe wakapenzegwa anze amulyango wamunzi, mukambo kakuti basalazye ibantu mukwindila mubulowa bwakwe.  
\v 13 Nkinkaako atwiinke kulinguwe kumbali amunzi, atubweze mawuse akwe.  
\v 14 Kambo tatukwe munzi wakukalilila pe ano, Pesi tuchiyandula munzi umbi uchiza.  
\v 15 Kwiinda mulinguwe, aboobo, tweelede chindi choonse tupede chipayizyo chakutembawula Leza, lumbayizya michelo yamilomo akuzumina muzina lyakwe.  
\v 16 Elyoo tutalubi nituluba mukuchita bubotu akwabilana, nkaambo mukwindila muchipayizyo chilobu Leza ulachibotelwa.  
\v 17 Kuswilila akulibombya kubazululi banu, eelyo mbembabo balanga myuya yanu mbuli abo bamupeda bukamboni bwaabo beni, Mulemeke kuchitila kuti bazuluzi banu bakachite echi chakubotelwa akutangunguna, pesi chakatali kumugwasya inywe.  
\v 18 Kamutukombela aswebo, nkambo twakombelezegwa munjisyoimbotu akuti twayandisya kukala muzintu zyoonse.  
\v 19 Ndilikumusungwazya nikuba nanka mukwindila mukuchita obu nkambo ndobozegwa kuli ndinywe mukufwambana.  
\v 20 Lino Leza waluumuno oyo wakabozya kuzwa kulufu mweembeli mupati wembelele, Mwami wesu Jesu, akubulowa bwachizuminano chitamani.  
\v 21 Kupa zyonse zibelesyo mukukusimya kuzintu zyoonse, mukubeleka mulindiswe kulecho chimubotezya, mukwindila muliJesu Kkilisito, kulinguwe akube bulemu kwalyoonse alyoonse. Ameni.  
\v 22 Lino ndamusungwazya, nobakwesu, ikuti mubweze ijwi eeli lyakumusungwazya ndindamulembela mubufwifwi.  
\v 23 Muzibe mukwesu Timoti wangununwa, ooyo ngwesizawe kuzomubona kuti afwambana kusika.  
\v 24 Mujuzye bazuluzi banu boonse antomwe abasalali abantu boonse baLeza. Abo bazwa kuItali balokumujuzya.  
\v 25 Luzyalo alube anywebo moonseni.   